{"tid":2023473,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港太多有錢人，問你服未？","createTime":"2020-05-19T04:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T12:00:11.000Z","uid":146880,"like":68,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"298736555bde3b2f2b3014b3b2e30f66c7b9610c","tid":2023473,"uid":146880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:44:16.000Z","msg":"Anthony Sir:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvqYkhw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmvqYkhw.jpg&h=a0bd827b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.businesstimes.com.hk/articles/127013/20200515/失業率高但樓市照反彈-兩大層面解釋為何那麼多人買樓-第一桶金.htm?fbclid=IwAR2HYUHEMTvORJvUV2-7oPUWWnMl-CXe_qt1toIEc_qhYUeP43GII-Q9ggk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstimes.com.hk%2Farticles%2F127013%2F20200515%2F%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%87%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%86%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E7%85%A7%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88-%E5%85%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A4%E9%9D%A2%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%82%A3%E9%BA%BC%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93-%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%A1%B6%E9%87%91.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2HYUHEMTvORJvUV2-7oPUWWnMl-CXe_qt1toIEc_qhYUeP43GII-Q9ggk&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=c2445c9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.businesstimes.com.hk/articles/127013/20200515/失業率高但樓市照反彈-兩大層面解釋為何那麼多人買樓-第一桶金.htm?fbclid=IwAR2HYUHEMTvORJvUV2-7oPUWWnMl-CXe_qt1toIEc_qhYUeP43GII-Q9ggk</a><br />\n<br />\n原文"},{"pid":"32c160439e9dbd109c3a42e6f21ed496c0fb302b","tid":2023473,"uid":115910,"like":126,"dislike":2,"score":124,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"身邊大把人上車,呢個世界好現實,就算供到仆街,點都係上左車先著數"},{"pid":"28464cdf64ac6cb7d1661e7f527fed9b9ccb3a64","tid":2023473,"uid":146880,"like":34,"dislike":5,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"32c160439e9dbd109c3a42e6f21ed496c0fb302b","tid":2023473,"uid":115910,"like":126,"dislike":2,"score":124,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"身邊大把人上車,呢個世界好現實,就算供到仆街,點都係上左車先著數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-